5:37:46.000Z","msg":"唔認同。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nWiki：<br />\n存在主義（英語：existentialism），是一個哲學的非理性主義思潮，它認為人存在的意義是無法經由理性思考而得到答案的，以強調個人、獨立自主和主觀經驗。<br />\n<br />\n歌詞唔強調個人自我，強調既反而係無我。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/15.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"992ef2567c8da115e3011baa2d4a818d20926266","tid":867348,"uid":12633,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T03:35:02.000Z","msg":"呢首歌唔係你所解既意思，至少唔係咁淺薄。<br />\n我相信作者都唔會同意你既解法，而作者自己都知道，其實唔解釋先係最好既解釋。<br />\n<br />\n道可道，非常道。"},{"pid":"bf1fb7e2f4e6a79a76beeccc1bd18e5f947efa37","tid":867348,"uid":188429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T05:46:52.000Z","msg":"解得唔錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nendy寫既歌真係好有意境<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fe388058fa99f5c5ed9888d4525382b166f6562","tid":867348,"uid":188429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T05:48:52.000Z","msg":"但係做人真係好難會完全臣服當下"},{"pid":"2a22efc09a78c8c60f05f9edf6d0f45007d132cf","tid":867348,"uid":76885,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"992ef2567c8da115e3011baa2d4a818d20926266","tid":867348,"uid":12633,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T03:35:02.000Z","msg":"呢首歌唔係你所解既意思，至少唔係咁淺薄。<br />\n我相信作者都唔會同意你既解法，而作者自己都知道，其實唔解釋先係最好既解釋。<br />\n<br />\n道可道，非常道。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T08:02:00.000Z","msg":"真，我就只能夠從自己既層次盡量理解文本。<br />\n我就理解唔到高層次過我既野。<br />\n<br />\n我唔肯定你層次係點。<br />\n可能比我近作者？<br />\n<br />\n不過你比我層次高，理解得多，但只願說道可道非常道，係讀者既損失 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6221fa799e0e0f9462873d71523f510af183a35","tid":867348,"uid":76885,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"0fe388058fa99f5c5ed9888d4525382b166f6562","tid":867348,"uid":188429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T05:48:52.000Z","msg":"但係做人真係好難會完全臣服當下"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T08:04:13.000Z","msg":"係一個理想。<br />\n到理想實現，又可能發覺理想非完美 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n就似：好鍾意一個人，追到返嚟，又覺其實唔係想像中咁神。<br />\n好多理想既野，只係FF中完美。<br />\n<br />\n全然臣服當下係其中一理想 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59169e2f4a4df5bd158833be76b4587179733e9d","tid":867348,"uid":76885,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"bf1fb7e2f4e6a79a76beeccc1bd18e5f947efa37","tid":867348,"uid":188429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T05:46:52.000Z","msg":"解得唔錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nendy寫既歌真係好有意境<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T08:04:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adc813e39bc262a70cd405e292b86c6bebf17e04","tid":867348,"uid":60028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T08:06:06.000Z","msg":"lm"}]}